EmailTemplate.name: SW: YP has withdrawn
EmailTemplate.subject: SW: YP has withdrawn, seek new match for SW
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi
{!Contact.Name} has withdrawn. Please urgently contact their SW to inform them and to begin seeking a new match.
Click on the link to view the record {!Contact.Link}
This is a standard email, sent automatically whenever a YP with a SW has withdrawn.
